		public threadForBrokenActivation: a reason: e ^<ThreadMirror> = (
			(* A broken thread over an existing simulated stack (a's thread), presenting the frames at the raise point. When [a] is not a simulated activation (eager evaluation paths), degrade to a frameless broken thread. *)

